=head1 DESCRIPTION

Represents membership rules in the document's ACL, defining how users
or groups are associated with access permissions.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Conditions => ArrayRef[L<Paws::QBusiness::DocumentAclCondition>]

An array of conditions that define the membership rules. Each condition
specifies criteria for users or groups to be included in this
membership.


=head2 MemberRelation => Str

The logical relation between members in the membership rule,
determining how multiple conditions are combined.



